PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of State (Housing) of Robert Gibelleau, of Laval, Quebec, as a director of the Board of Directors of Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective April 1, 1991, in the place of Richard Lebeau.
